2. DB 설계
	http://aquerytool.com/ 을 이용하여 er diagram 작성
	
	DB 접속
		cmd
		> cd C:\Bitnami\wampstack-5.6.30-2\mysql\bin
		> mysql -h127.0.0.1 -p3306 -uroot -pQwer1234
		> CREATE DATABASE fashion CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_general_ci;
		> use fashion;
		
